{"tid":20094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"載8具骸骨兼有北韓鈔票　詭異木船漂到日本","createTime":"2016-12-03T07:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-12T18:39:28.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e92c6888d80d6d69563150b93e2166dd094fdca","tid":20094,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:26:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161203/photo/bknint-20161203060445704-1203_17011_001_04b.jpg?20161203144749\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161203%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20161203060445704-1203_17011_001_04b.jpg%3F20161203144749&h=de3b7af5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本京都府舞鶴市警方在附近海岸發現一艘木船，船上有8具骸骨、以及相信是北韓的鈔票，目前正調查該艘船是否由北韓漂流到日本海域。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161203/photo/bknint-20161203060445704-1203_17011_001_03b.jpg?20161203144749\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161203%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20161203060445704-1203_17011_001_03b.jpg%3F20161203144749&h=ef234d82&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舞鶴市海岸警衞隊表示，一艘漁船船長周二報稱在離岸7公里的地方，發現一艘木船漂流，事隔一日，當局發現該艘木船，並檢查船上和周邊。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20161203/photo/bknint-20161203060445704-1203_17011_001_02b.jpg?20161203144749\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161203%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20161203060445704-1203_17011_001_02b.jpg%3F20161203144749&h=6e0628a5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n木船長12米、闊3米，當局更在船上發現捕魚用具、北韓鈔票及8具骸骨，惟部分骸骨殘缺不全，其中只有3份頭蓋骨，7份骨盤，其後才在附近海底找到另外2份頭蓋骨及骨盤。日本海域包括青森縣和新潟縣，經常發現疑似北韓的船隻衝上岸，當局表示正調查該船是否與之有關，並會鑑定人骨。 <br />\n<br />\n過往有不少疑似北韓的木船漂往日本海岸，去年10月到11月期間，北海道、青森縣到福井縣之間的5縣沿岸，至少出現11艘殘舊木船。船上合計總共藏有多達25具腐屍，船身均寫有韓文，甚至其中兩艘寫上「朝鮮人民軍」。但報道指船內有釣針及漁網等漁具，推斷並非軍用船隻。 <br />\n<br />\n日媒報道指，自2013年至2015年間，已於海岸發現逾175艘疑為北韓漁船的木船。有專家表示，可能是北韓漁民在裝備不齊全的情況下出海捕魚，結果遭遇海難，船隻則漂流至日本海域。"},{"pid":"009a20f31c611ef4b8cb958e53b7583a7a45e690","tid":20094,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:36:35.000Z","msg":"Nice boat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2cb0e3a7a41776eaea796d62a26f2a5d44d74ca","tid":20094,"uid":13809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:40:26.000Z","msg":"家明？"},{"pid":"88497a461ff9ddb804984bce02af54434391e1e3","tid":20094,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:40:56.000Z","msg":"鬼船<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0438cea2350cd3e9d282d488ae5420322855f8ba","tid":20094,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T07:47:07.000Z","msg":"黑珍珠號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d823c4106ed408a9be80c621f8e139a54db8b79d","tid":20094,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-11T19:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1825723091ba7f80eb0876cdc2786410a9a204b1","tid":20094,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-11T23:12:03.000Z","msg":"好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3137d92bea547beeb68adec0b5af5989011e019c","tid":20094,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-11T23:43:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n行行下隻船神左 叫天不應叫地不聞<br />\n其實do冇乜野恐怖, 好左漂左去日本"},{"pid":"c1c588af165f874216964d0b6488374d4041e455","tid":20094,"uid":38588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-11T23:47:10.000Z","msg":"來生不做北韓人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"733619385cbf1c05a3e5d2d615ae05b8f62476cb","tid":20094,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-11T2